And try to make sure that the task in your action depends on the regular add_kernel task from moose. You can do it like this in your app source file:
static void
associateSyntaxInner(Syntax & syntax, ActionFactory & /*action_factory*/)
{
  ...
  ...
  // add Kernels action
  registerTask("add_myapp_kernels", /*is_required=*/false);
  addTaskDependency("add_myapp_kernel", "add_kernel");
  ...
  ...
}

which assumes that you change this line in your action source file:
registerMooseAction("myApp", myKernelAction, "add_kernel");

to
registerMooseAction("myApp", myKernelAction, "add_myapp_kernel");

